  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of Mapracorat Ophthalmic
      Suspension, 3% to vehicle for the treatment of postoperative inflammation and pain following
      cataract surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
